The losses are computed from the outputs:
Decoder тЖТ reconstructs x_t тЖТ image loss
Reward head тЖТ predicts r_t тЖТ reward loss
RSSM тЖТ prior vs posterior тЖТ KL loss
All these losses are summed (with coefficients) to make the total world model loss.



   +-------------------+
   |   Environment     |
   +-------------------+
           |
        obs x_t
           |
        Encoder
           |
        RSSM (h_t, z_t)
          /      \
      Decoder   RewardHead/ValueHead
          |
    Reconstructed obs
          |
      WorldModel Loss
           |
       (update world model)
           |
      Actor + Critic
          |
      Imagination rollouts
           |
        Policy update

